Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===================Pre===================
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.43,0:00:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和渚小姐是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.14,0:00:22.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾 病因不明
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.41,0:00:27.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但恐怕会和渚小姐一样 今后也一直…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.55,0:00:33.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明刚才还那么精神
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.17,0:00:42.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我就此作别
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.42,0:00:58.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋也
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.16,0:01:02.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的父亲是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.95,0:01:04.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.17,0:01:07.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么你就要振作
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===================OP===================
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.94,0:01:35.37,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}熟悉的坡道上 却已不见你的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.53,0:01:41.05,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}柔和的阳光 透过树叶投下斑点
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.13,0:01:46.28,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}我独自一人 伫立在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.32,0:01:53.59,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}回顾着那些 温暖的往事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.09,0:02:01.71,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}只有你 只有你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.78,0:02:07.78,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}在变幻的时间中 永驻我心底
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.88,0:02:15.55,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}风吹而过 泪水渗眼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.66,0:02:22.59,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}你的身影 已变得更远
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.66,0:02:24.70,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}任何时候都不会忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.70,0:02:26.87,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}哪怕一切的一切全部改变
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.87,0:02:29.08,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}不忘记那一件 那一件
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.08,0:02:31.46,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}稀松平常之事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.49,0:02:32.57,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}终会让你看到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.57,0:02:35.79,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}那被光芒包裹着的唯一
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.79,0:02:37.85,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}守护 守护
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.85,0:02:40.89,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,500)\be1}直到永远
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===================Text===================
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.16,0:02:52.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吗 你不冷吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.49,0:02:56.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身为人偶的我感受不到寒冷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.26,0:03:00.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是她的手 一定已经冰凉了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.07,0:03:04.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我连那手的冷暖也感觉不到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.39,0:03:10.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快世界就将一片雪白了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.17,0:03:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要抓紧一点了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.39,0:03:29.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,运动会？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.35,0:03:35.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 不去跑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.05,0:03:38.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天会一直陪在你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.31,0:03:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿秋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.50,0:03:42.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔可能会去跑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.64,0:03:46.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两名最后一棒都缺席的话 临时找代跑会很麻烦的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.15,0:03:52.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 赢过阿秋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.50,0:03:55.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说了会陪在你身边了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.61,0:03:58.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.56,0:04:00.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是站在我这边的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.45,0:04:03.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是站在你这边的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.76,0:04:06.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管发生什么事 都会守护你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.13,0:04:14.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,困了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.63,0:04:18.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧 我哪也不会去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.34,0:04:26.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一周 两周
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.43,0:04:29.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个月过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.34,0:04:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐的高烧依然没有退
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.44,0:04:36.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去不了幼儿园 连房间都无力走出
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.44,0:04:38.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.65,0:04:44.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不希望冈崎君辞职的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.33,0:04:47.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你也有你的难处啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.31,0:04:57.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下了决心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.08,0:05:03.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早苗和大叔都阻止我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.23,0:05:06.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我想陪在汐的身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.51,0:05:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有存款吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.95,0:05:09.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.51,0:05:12.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在为汐存着学费的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.65,0:05:13.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.76,0:05:16.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.76,0:05:19.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今为止 多谢关照了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.77,0:05:28.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿去 别丢了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.59,0:05:31.50,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芳野
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.36,0:05:33.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这方便吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.75,0:05:35.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎可能方便啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.54,0:05:37.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天起 工作时会很困扰的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.69,0:05:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.98,0:05:43.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为交换 把你的螺丝刀借来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.87,0:05:45.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回来时再还你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.85,0:05:49.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小汐身体变好了 就回来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.95,0:05:51.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螺丝刀那时再还
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.65,0:06:15.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会好好用它的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.42,0:06:23.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐一直留在家里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.00,0:06:26.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然考虑过住院 但最后还是没去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.58,0:06:31.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然不知道治疗方法 去了医院也意义不大
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.95,0:06:36.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最重要的是 汐想要留在家里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.90,0:06:39.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡衣换成新的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.29,0:06:43.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用站起来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.81,0:06:45.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸来帮你换衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.27,0:06:48.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人就做得到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.89,0:07:01.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.94,0:07:03.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在一个人做不到也没事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.21,0:07:08.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐已经无法独自换衣服了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.59,0:07:10.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也无法独自上厕所
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.45,0:07:13.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三餐只能吃些柔质食物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.67,0:07:19.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平和的日子 已经再也回不来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.35,0:07:30.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐 有想要的东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.52,0:07:33.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有的话就说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.63,0:07:36.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩具 零食 什么都能给你买来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.26,0:07:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.33,0:07:44.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅行？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.17,0:07:46.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想和爸爸再去旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.83,0:07:50.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种事 一点也不快活吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.15,0:07:53.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸心情不好 还大喊大叫了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.19,0:07:55.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快活
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.35,0:07:57.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想再去旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.83,0:08:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐上火车 和爸爸两人一起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.83,0:08:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等身体好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.51,0:08:08.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在 就想去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.69,0:08:14.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐 别这么不讲理 让爸爸为难啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.20,0:08:24.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我连独生女的…唯一的愿望都无法满足吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.55,0:08:29.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渚 我该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.98,0:08:32.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种时候 如果你还在的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.63,0:08:40.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我们一家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.80,0:08:43.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是被这小镇玩弄于股掌之上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.38,0:08:48.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩笑般地给予幸福 又将它轻易夺走
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.08,0:08:56.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可饶恕 汐绝对要救回来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.22,0:08:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对要救汐…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.22,0:09:03.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烦请关照了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.42,0:09:05.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢走
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.31,0:09:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.89,0:09:11.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.25,0:09:15.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.21,0:09:20.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎能收下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.83,0:09:22.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这么倔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.71,0:09:25.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是那个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.53,0:09:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还有存款 再撑一段时间没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.50,0:09:30.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敢撒谎的话老子灭了你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.59,0:09:31.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.31,0:09:34.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.68,0:09:40.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使做为男人的颜面尽失 有些东西也要死死守住
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.98,0:09:41.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.67,0:09:44.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.90,0:09:46.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的不行了会说的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.44,0:10:12.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抽吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.21,0:10:15.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我戒了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.34,0:10:17.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很明智
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.52,0:10:21.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.26,0:10:27.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人们牺牲了这里原有的自然 建起了这医院
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.10,0:10:30.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面又会拿什么作为牺牲品呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.10,0:10:36.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,镇郊的山丘在被挖掉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.77,0:10:40.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像要建购物中心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.71,0:10:43.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生活会更便利 对居民来说是好事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.01,0:10:47.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.42,0:10:51.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你将濒死的渚带到这里的那一刻起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.53,0:10:55.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许渚就和这个小镇紧密相连了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.92,0:10:58.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 渚的孩子汐也…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.66,0:11:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不断变化 样貌的改变
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.10,0:11:08.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对小镇来说是种痛苦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.09,0:11:14.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和痛苦无关吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.55,0:11:21.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「啊 真的在不断改变啊」不就是这种感觉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.53,0:11:26.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果人的逝去 也只是无数变化中的一种
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.85,0:11:30.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就只能乖乖认命吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.59,0:11:35.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为不想那样 人们才会建起医院这种东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.39,0:11:56.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给予这小镇与住民…以幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.15,0:12:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,口渴了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.96,0:12:49.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝水吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.31,0:13:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水很凉 要慢慢喝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.69,0:13:05.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一口气喝下去会喝坏肚子的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.94,0:13:15.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.64,0:13:16.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.72,0:13:17.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.82,0:13:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想去旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.06,0:13:27.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等病好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.89,0:13:29.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.45,0:13:32.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再去那片花田好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.87,0:13:35.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是现在去北方有点冷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.88,0:13:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去南边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.40,0:13:40.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去又温暖 又热闹 空气清新的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.35,0:13:42.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.14,0:13:43.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在 就想去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.96,0:13:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等病好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.46,0:13:49.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是说了好几次吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.63,0:13:54.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在 现在就想去 花田
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.24,0:13:56.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.43,0:13:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是现在不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.91,0:14:03.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想和爸爸一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.09,0:14:16.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.44,0:14:19.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就如你所愿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.85,0:14:25.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 身体难受要马上说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.39,0:14:28.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.55,0:14:36.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我背你 来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.23,0:14:39.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.57,0:14:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别勉强了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.54,0:14:45.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想和爸爸一起走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.63,0:14:46.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.90,0:14:49.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 一起能走多远就走多远吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.71,0:14:54.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出发吧 来踏上快乐的旅程吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.30,0:15:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧吗 汐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.06,0:15:17.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的身体难受的话 要马上说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.04,0:15:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可要去看医生呐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.46,0:15:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐 已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.26,0:16:01.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是雪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.45,0:16:18.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐喜欢雪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.12,0:16:22.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 爸爸也喜欢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.36,0:16:24.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.98,0:16:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸也喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.39,0:16:34.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走得动吗 汐 歇一会儿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.44,0:16:38.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁着没下大 搭辆车吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.37,0:16:40.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来背你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.18,0:16:41.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.98,0:17:34.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.40,0:17:50.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.68,0:17:52.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 汐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.17,0:17:55.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在 在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.62,0:17:57.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经在火车上了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.38,0:18:01.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经在火车上了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.01,0:18:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好暗 到晚上了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.32,0:18:08.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 深夜了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.97,0:18:10.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.02,0:18:12.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.44,0:18:15.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最喜欢了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.61,0:18:20.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 爸爸也最喜欢汐了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.98,0:18:35.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐？ 汐？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.61,0:18:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.19,0:19:02.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 我不要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.65,0:19:07.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渚 救救汐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.44,0:19:11.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渚！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.15,0:19:16.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁来…谁来救救汐！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.58,0:19:20.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渚…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.97,0:19:57.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.75,0:20:14.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再走几步才能到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.36,0:20:18.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经到了只差一步的地方了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.39,0:20:24.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是说 仍有无尽的路途等在前方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.30,0:20:54.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我讨厌这小镇
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.18,0:21:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里充满了我想忘却的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.19,0:21:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天上学 和朋友聊聊 再回到不想回的家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.57,0:21:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去 会迎来什么变化么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.18,0:21:20.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会迎来改变的那一天吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.45,0:21:33.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豆沙面包
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.41,0:21:37.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢这所学校吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.55,0:21:43.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我非常非常喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.54,0:21:47.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是一切的一切 都无法不做改变
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.02,0:21:52.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果在这里搭话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.99,0:21:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会和渚相识 再开始交往
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.80,0:22:00.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 不这么做更好不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.38,0:22:02.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有相识更好…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===================ED===================
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.69,0:22:26.07,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}双眼凝视着 流动的云朵
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.24,0:22:32.99,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}心中感受着 天空变幻的色彩
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.74,0:22:41.18,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}伫立不前的我们 察觉到了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.32,0:22:48.20,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}这变迁的世界编织出的歌曲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.32,0:22:55.44,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}伸出的指尖 不断寻找着
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.44,0:23:04.13,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}那恒久不变的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.35,0:23:11.69,ed2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}举起的手中火炬闪亮
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.86,0:23:19.42,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}那是通向明天的小小路标
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.42,0:23:26.75,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}现在也在不断回响
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.93,0:23:34.28,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}那一天的话语 终将化为誓言
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.43,0:23:39.04,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,500)}推动我前行
